snippet.title: Arcadian Atlas Teaser
snippet.description:
Arcadian Atlas, a Tactics RPG about the choices people make in pursuit of the things they love, and the havoc it wreaks on a kingdom.

Kickstarter coming April 5th! Subscribe to the Newsletter: http://eepurl.com/bqmphP

(Video features alpha footage - everything subject to change.)
